# EventType: 2812470000
# Descriptor: [e+ e- -> J/psi [-> mu+ mu-] X->[D*+ D*-]->[D0 pi+]->[D0->K- pi+ pi+ pi-]]
# NickName: ee_Jpsi_DstDst_mumu_D02K3pi
# Documentation: Double charmonium production.
# Tested:Yes 
# PhysicsWG: Quarkonium
# Responsible: Jiyuan Zhang
