# Cuts: None
# Date: 20260128

Alias Myjpsi J/psi
Alias myD*+ D*+
Alias myD*- D*-

Alias myD0  D0
Alias myantiD0  anti-D0


Decay vpho
1.00  Myjpsi  X4160    PHSP;
Enddecay

Decay X4160
0.5 myD*+ D*-    PHSP;
0.5 D*+ myD*-    PHSP;
Enddecay

Decay Myjpsi
1.00   mu+ mu-            PHOTOS VLL;
Enddecay

Decay myD*+
1.00  myD0  pi+          PHOTOS PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay myD*-

Decay myD0
1.00    K-  pi+  pi+  pi-    PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay myantiD0

End

